---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.jsx';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import StructuredData from '../components/StructuredData.astro';
import ContactInfo from '../components/ContactInfo.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Websites for Creatives & Hospitality NZ | Own Your Audience | YourHQ"
  description="Done-for-you websites for NZ cafés, salons, photographers & yoga studios. Built in 5 days. Stop renting your audience from Instagram. From $347.50 (Founding Offer)."
>
  <StructuredData slot="head" />

  <!-- Announcement Bar -->
  <div class="bg-hibiscus text-white text-center py-3 px-4 text-sm font-mono tracking-widest uppercase border-b border-white/10 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/20 animate-pulse"></div>
    <span class="relative z-10">⏳ Founding Offer Ends March 31: <strong>50% Off All Builds</strong> + Rate Locked for Life | Code: <strong>FOUNDING26</strong></span>
  </div>

  <!-- Navbar -->
  <Navbar client:load />

  <main>
    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="relative pt-20 pb-24 md:pt-32 md:pb-40 border-b border-carbon bg-[size:40px_40px] bg-grid-pattern">
        <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

          <div class="max-w-5xl">
            <!-- Badge -->
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 border-2 border-carbon bg-white shadow-hard-sm mb-8">
              <span class="flex h-3 w-3 relative">
                <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-hibiscus opacity-75"></span>
                <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-3 w-3 bg-hibiscus"></span>
              </span>
              <span class="text-xs font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-carbon">Cafés • Salons • Photographers • Studios</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Headline -->
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] mb-8">
              Your Work Deserves a Home That Isn't <br/>
              <span class="text-hibiscus">Someone Else's App.</span>
            </h1>

            <!-- Subhead -->
            <div class="border-l-4 border-carbon pl-6 mb-10 max-w-3xl">
                <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium leading-relaxed text-carbon/90 mb-4">
                  Instagram can change its algorithm tomorrow. Your account can be hacked. But a website is yours forever. 
                </p>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                  A website that actually brings in bookings, enquiries, and new clients — not just likes. Built in 5 days. One 15-minute vibe chat. We handle the rest.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- CTAs -->
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 items-start">
              <a href="#offer" class="bg-carbon text-white px-8 py-5 text-center border-2 border-carbon shadow-hard hover:shadow-none hover:translate-y-[4px] transition-all font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm md:text-base">
                Claim Founding Deal (50% Off)
              </a>
              <a href="#process" class="bg-white text-carbon px-8 py-5 text-center border-2 border-carbon shadow-hard-sm hover:shadow-none hover:translate-y-[2px] transition-all font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm md:text-base">
                See How It Works
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TRUSTED BY -->
    <section class="py-10 bg-white border-b border-carbon">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8">
        <p class="text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400">Trusted by NZ Creatives</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-10 md:gap-16">
          <img src="/rumours-logo.webp" alt="Rumours on Rust" class="h-8 md:h-12 object-contain grayscale opacity-60 hover:grayscale-0 hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300" />
          <img src="/emberandice-logo.webp" alt="Ember and Ice" class="h-8 md:h-12 object-contain grayscale opacity-60 hover:grayscale-0 hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 1: THE PROBLEM (RENTED VS OWNED) -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-carbon text-paper border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter leading-tight mb-6">
                You Built Something Beautiful.<br/>
                <span class="text-frangipani">But You Built It On Rented Land.</span>
              </h2>
              <div class="space-y-6 text-lg font-light text-gray-300 mt-8">
                <p>Instagram is an amazing tool. But it's not your business. It's a platform you rent — and the landlord changes the rules whenever they feel like it.</p>
                <p>When the algorithm shifts, your reach drops. When your account gets flagged, your bookings stop. When a new client Googles your business name instead of searching social media — <strong class="text-white font-medium">they find nothing.</strong></p>
                <p>You've worked incredibly hard to build your craft and your reputation. A website means you finally own your audience, show up on Google, and take bookings while you sleep.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Rented vs Owned UI Card -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 transform rotate-1 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500">
              <!-- Rented -->
              <div class="bg-gray-900 border-2 border-gray-700 p-6 shadow-hard-white">
                <span class="text-xs font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-hibiscus mb-4 block">The App (Rented)</span>
                <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
                  <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-red-400">✗</span> Algorithm decides who sees you</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-red-400">✗</span> Can't take deposits properly</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-red-400">✗</span> Doesn't show up in local Google searches</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-red-400">✗</span> Account can be suspended overnight</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <!-- Owned -->
              <div class="bg-white text-carbon border-2 border-white p-6 shadow-hard-white -ml-2 sm:-ml-8 mt-4 sm:mt-8 relative z-10">
                <span class="text-xs font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-signal mb-4 block flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-signal rounded-full animate-pulse"></span> Your Website (Owned)
                </span>
                <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-700 font-medium">
                  <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-signal font-bold">✓</span> You own the traffic and the data</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-signal font-bold">✓</span> Direct bookings and payments</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-signal font-bold">✓</span> Ranks on Google for "Near Me" searches</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-signal font-bold">✓</span> Looks like an established, premium business</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 2: THE VIBE MATCH -->
    <section class="bg-paper border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2">

            <!-- Left: Visual (Polaroid Style) -->
            <div class="bg-carbon border-r border-carbon p-12 md:p-24 flex items-center justify-center min-h-[500px] relative overflow-hidden">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[size:20px_20px] bg-grid-pattern opacity-20"></div>
              
              <!-- Polaroid Frame -->
              <div class="relative w-full max-w-sm bg-white p-4 pb-16 border-2 border-carbon shadow-hard-white group z-10 transform -rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition-all duration-500">
                <div class="aspect-square bg-gray-100 border-2 border-carbon overflow-hidden">
                  <img src="/creatives-hero.webp" alt="Creative business owner" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700 scale-105 group-hover:scale-100" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentElement.innerHTML='<div class=\'w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100\'><div class=\'text-center p-8\'><p class=\'text-6xl mb-4\'>🎨</p></div></div>'" />
                </div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-5 left-0 w-full text-center font-mono text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-carbon">
                  100% On Brand
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Right: The Content -->
            <div class="p-8 md:p-24 flex flex-col justify-center bg-white">
              <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter mb-8 leading-tight">
                A Website That Actually <br/>
                <span class="text-hibiscus">Feels Like You.</span>
              </h2>

              <div class="prose text-carbon space-y-6 text-lg">
                <p>Here's what stops most creatives from getting a website: the fear it'll look generic. Template-y. Like everyone else's. You've spent years building a distinct aesthetic — and you'd rather have no website than one that kills the vibe.</p>
                <p>We get it. <strong>So we start with a conversation about your vibe before we touch a single pixel.</strong></p>
                <p class="text-gray-500">We look at your space, your Instagram feed, and your brand colours. We build websites that feel like a digital extension of your physical business — not a cookie-cutter template.</p>

                <div class="p-6 border-l-4 border-hibiscus bg-paper mt-8">
                    <p class="font-extrabold text-xl mb-2">You don't need to be a designer.</p>
                    <p class="text-base text-gray-700">Total time from you: one 15-minute vibe chat. We handle the rest.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 3: THE PROCESS -->
    <section id="process" class="py-24 bg-paper border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-16">
            <div class="md:col-span-5">
               <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter leading-tight sticky top-24">
                Built in 5 Days.<br/>
                Zero Homework.<br/>
                <span class="text-gray-400">Seriously.</span>
              </h2>
              <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mt-6 leading-relaxed">
                You're already working 50 hours a week on your craft. You don't have time to spend your weekend fighting with Squarespace.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-7 space-y-0 mt-8 md:mt-0">
              <!-- Step 1 -->
              <div class="flex gap-6 md:gap-8 pb-16 border-l-2 border-carbon pl-8 md:pl-12 relative">
                <div class="absolute -left-4 top-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-signal border-4 border-paper flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xs">1</div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">The Vibe Chat (15 mins)</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    A quick 15-minute conversation — between clients, on your lunch break, or after a shift. We ask about your style, your customers, your story. You don't write anything down.
                  </p>
                  <span class="inline-block bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs font-mono font-bold uppercase border border-carbon shadow-hard-sm">No Typing Required</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Step 2 -->
              <div class="flex gap-6 md:gap-8 pb-16 border-l-2 border-carbon pl-8 md:pl-12 relative">
                <div class="absolute -left-4 top-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-carbon border-4 border-paper flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xs">2</div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">We Do the Digging (0 mins)</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    We pull your best photos from Instagram, Facebook, and Google. We write the copy. We research your story. No chasing files, no sending messy Dropbox links.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Step 3 -->
              <div class="flex gap-6 md:gap-8 pb-16 border-l-2 border-carbon pl-8 md:pl-12 relative">
                <div class="absolute -left-4 top-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-hibiscus border-4 border-paper flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xs">3</div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">The Factory Build (Days 1-4)</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    We build your site — custom design that matches your aesthetic, mobile-first (because your clients are on their phones), booking integrations, gallery, the lot.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Step 4 -->
              <div class="flex gap-6 md:gap-8 border-l-2 border-transparent pl-8 md:pl-12 relative">
                <div class="absolute -left-4 top-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-frangipani border-4 border-paper flex items-center justify-center text-carbon font-bold text-xs">4</div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">Preview on Day 5 (Love it or Refund)</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    We send a private preview link. If it doesn't feel right, we fix it. If you don't love it at all, full refund of your setup fee (minus ~3% processing + any domain costs).
                  </p>
                  <span class="inline-block bg-carbon text-white px-3 py-1 text-xs font-mono font-bold uppercase border border-carbon shadow-hard-sm">Risk-Free Launch</span>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 4: THE MATH (ROI DOCKET) -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-carbon border-b border-carbon relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
            
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tighter mb-4">
                    The Cost of Being Invisible
                </h2>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-400">The question isn't "can I afford a website?" <br/>It's "can I afford to keep losing clients to competitors who have one?"</p>
            </div>

            <!-- The Docket UI -->
            <div class="bg-white p-8 md:p-12 shadow-hard-white border-t-8 border-hibiscus relative mx-auto max-w-2xl">
                
                <div class="text-center mb-8 border-b-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 pb-8">
                    <p class="font-mono text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Lost Revenue Docket</p>
                    <p class="font-bold text-2xl text-carbon">Creative & Hospitality</p>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2">DATE: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>
                </div>

                <div class="space-y-4 font-mono text-sm md:text-base text-carbon border-b-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 pb-8 mb-8">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-end">
                        <span class="text-gray-600">Quiet Saturday at Salon (4 missed clients)</span>
                        <span class="font-bold border-b border-gray-200 border-dotted flex-1 mx-4 mb-1"></span>
                        <span class="font-bold text-red-500">-$400</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-end">
                        <span class="text-gray-600">Photographer missed one wedding booking</span>
                        <span class="font-bold border-b border-gray-200 border-dotted flex-1 mx-4 mb-1"></span>
                        <span class="font-bold text-red-500">-$2,500</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-end">
                        <span class="text-gray-600">Café losing locals to place with a menu online</span>
                        <span class="font-bold border-b border-gray-200 border-dotted flex-1 mx-4 mb-1"></span>
                        <span class="font-bold text-red-500">Ongoing</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="pt-6 mt-6 border-t border-gray-100"></div>
                    
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-end text-lg">
                        <span class="font-bold text-signal">YourHQ Launch (With FOUNDING26)</span>
                        <span class="font-bold border-b border-gray-200 border-dotted flex-1 mx-4 mb-1"></span>
                        <span class="font-bold text-signal">$497.50 Setup</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-paper p-6 text-center border border-carbon/10">
                    <p class="text-xl font-extrabold text-carbon mb-2">Breakeven = ~1 extra booking.</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">One new client who finds you on Google pays for the entire build. Everything else is profit.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION: WHAT WE BUILD FOR YOU -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter leading-tight mb-8">
                Everything Your Business Needs Online. <br/>
                <span class="text-signal">Nothing You Have to Manage.</span>
              </h2>

              <div class="prose text-carbon space-y-6 text-lg">
                <p>You want bookings. You want to show up on Google. You want something that looks as good as your Instagram — without the platform risk.</p>
                <p class="font-extrabold text-2xl text-carbon pt-6 border-t border-carbon/10">
                  We build it. We maintain it. You just do your work.
                </p>
                <p>Need to update your menu? Got new portfolio shots? Just text us. We handle the changes — no logins, no confusing page builders, no drama.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-paper p-8 md:p-12 border-2 border-carbon shadow-hard">
                <p class="font-mono font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-hibiscus mb-8">Built For Your Kind of Business</p>
                <ul class="space-y-5">
                    <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
                        <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded bg-carbon text-white flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><span class="text-sm">✓</span></div>
                        <span class="font-medium text-lg">Mobile-first design — clients browse on their phones</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
                        <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded bg-carbon text-white flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><span class="text-sm">✓</span></div>
                        <span class="font-medium text-lg">Online booking integration (Fresha, Timely, etc.)</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
                        <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded bg-carbon text-white flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><span class="text-sm">✓</span></div>
                        <span class="font-medium text-lg">Portfolio & gallery pages that show your work properly</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
                        <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded bg-carbon text-white flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><span class="text-sm">✓</span></div>
                        <span class="font-medium text-lg">Menu / service list / pricing display</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
                        <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded bg-carbon text-white flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><span class="text-sm">✓</span></div>
                        <span class="font-medium text-lg">Google Business Profile setup & optimisation</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
                        <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded bg-hibiscus text-white flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><span class="text-sm">✓</span></div>
                        <span class="font-bold text-lg text-hibiscus">Annual design refresh included</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION: PRICING WITH FOUNDING MEMBER OFFER -->
    <section id="offer" class="py-24 bg-paper border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

          <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
             <div class="inline-block bg-hibiscus text-white px-4 py-1 text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 animate-pulse">
               Ending March 31, 2026
             </div>
             <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter mb-6">Founding Member Offer</h2>
             <p class="text-xl text-carbon/80 leading-relaxed">
               50% Off All Builds. Monthly rates locked for life. <br/>
               <strong class="text-hibiscus">Strictly 26 spots remaining.</strong>
             </p>
          </div>

          <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto">
             <!-- Launch Package Card (Sweet spot for creatives) -->
             <div class="p-8 md:p-10 border-4 border-carbon bg-white flex flex-col relative shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_#111111] transform md:-rotate-1 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-300">

                <div class="absolute -top-5 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-carbon text-white px-6 py-2 font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs shadow-sm whitespace-nowrap">
                    Sweet Spot for Creatives
                </div>

                <div class="text-center mb-8 mt-4 border-b border-gray-100 pb-8">
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-2">The Launch</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-500">Professional 5-Page Vibe-Matched Site</p>
                </div>

                <!-- PRICING STACK -->
                <div class="text-center mb-8">
                    <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                        <span class="text-gray-400 line-through decoration-2 text-xl font-bold">$995</span>
                        <span class="text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter text-signal">$497<span class="text-3xl">.50</span></span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">+ GST SETUP (ONE-OFF)</p>
                    
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mt-6 bg-gray-50 py-3 rounded border border-gray-200">
                        <span class="text-xl font-bold text-carbon">$149</span>
                        <span class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs">/mo + GST (Locked for Life)</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-1">
                    <li class="flex gap-3 text-sm font-medium"><span class="text-signal font-bold">✓</span> 5-page professional website</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3 text-sm font-medium"><span class="text-signal font-bold">✓</span> 15-minute vibe chat (no homework)</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3 text-sm font-medium"><span class="text-signal font-bold">✓</span> Domain + hosting included</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3 text-sm font-medium"><span class="text-signal font-bold">✓</span> Booking integration (Fresha, etc)</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3 text-sm font-bold bg-signal/10 px-2 py-1 -mx-2"><span class="text-signal">✓</span> Annual design refresh included</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3 text-sm font-bold bg-signal/10 px-2 py-1 -mx-2"><span class="text-signal">✓</span> Unlimited text/photo updates</li>
                </ul>

                <div class="mb-6 p-4 border-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 bg-gray-50 text-center relative group">
                    <p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Use Code at Checkout:</p>
                    <p class="text-2xl font-mono font-bold text-carbon">FOUNDING26</p>
                </div>

                <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/00waEWh0S14s3xH4UzdZ600" class="w-full block bg-signal text-white text-center py-5 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-carbon transition-colors text-lg shadow-hard-sm hover:shadow-none hover:translate-y-[2px]">
                    Claim 50% Off Build
                </a>
                
                <p class="text-center text-xs mt-6 text-gray-500 font-mono">
                    "Love Your Launch" Guarantee:<br/>Full refund if you don't love the preview.
                </p>
             </div>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center mt-12">
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-2">Need more pages? A full portfolio, blog, or multi-location setup? The Growth plan ($747.50 setup) gives you a 7-page site.</p>
            <a href="/pricing" class="text-carbon font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs hover:text-signal transition-colors border-b border-carbon hover:border-signal pb-1">Compare all plans</a>
          </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION: REAL TALK / FAQ -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white border-b border-carbon">
